  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "关于新上铁路恩格阿娄、布日奇会让站及配套扩能改造工程项目[]用地选址范围内文物勘查验收许可的请示",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "center",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "乌审旗文物局[]：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "为贯彻落实《内蒙古自治区“十四五”铁路专用线实施方案》，保障国家能源安全，释放区域优质煤炭产能，满足下游企业用煤需求，依据《改建铁路新上线扩能改造工程可行性研究的会议纪要》（纪要〔2021〕4号），我司已委托三门峡市文物考古勘探有限公司开展新上铁路恩格阿娄、布日奇会让站及配套扩能改造工程项目区域考古勘探工作（项目代码：2502-150626-04-02-262369）[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "该项目分别于既有新上铁路K90+040、K117+200处增开恩格阿娄、布日奇2座预留车站，新申请用地6.71公顷（其中恩格阿娄站3.62公顷、布日奇站3.09公顷）；到发线采用60kg/m钢轨，铺轨7.44公里；房屋总建筑面积3445平方米；两站均设到发线2条（含正线1条），有效长均满足1700米，各设50×6×0.3m客运站台1座；远期均预留双线建设条件，铁路等级为Ⅰ级[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "根据《内蒙古自治区文物局关于做好基本建设用地考古工作的通知》（内文物发〔2025〕6号）要求，三门峡市文物考古勘探有限公司已完成项目所在区域实地考古勘查工作，并编制形成《考古勘探报告》[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "为加快项目建设进度，完善前期手续，现提请贵局对该项目用地选址范围内的文物勘查验收许可事项予以审议，并依法批准，以便推进工程顺利实施[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "妥否，请批示。",
